message.content:
I need to identify the capital contributed by shareholders in exchange for shares from the balance sheet.

Looking at the balance sheet, the line item that represents capital contributed by shareholders is "Paid-in Capital."

The initial value of Paid-in Capital as of 2023-12-31 is 16000000.00.
The ending value of Paid-in Capital as of 2024-02-01 is 16000000.00.

This represents the amount of capital that shareholders contributed to the company in exchange for shares. The value remained unchanged between the initial and end dates.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '16000000.00', 'end value': '16000000.00'}}
```
